      "name": "**The SOUL**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**The SOUL**\n\nThe SOUL is a physical, though invisible thing that all beings possess, though with variations. It is the 'conduit' for magic. The fundamental property of the SOUL is 'equal exchange'. That is, all magic potential is drawn from the soul. Just like in physics, every action has an equal and opposite reaction. In this case, magic users damage their own SOUL an amount proportional to the magic used, though the SOUL is capable of recovery. The SOUL is also the very 'core' of all thinking creatures, with the brain being only a receiver for what the SOUL thinks.",
