      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Mana**\n\nMana is an abstraction of the actual reality, which is that the SOUL has only a set amount of damage it can take in a short period before shattering. However, this term is widely used due to most magic users not truly understanding the principle of equal exchange, instead believing it to be 'mana'.",
