    {
      "id": "2cca68ed-7e2d-4e13-b2b2-126f853ab910",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Passion**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Passion**\n\n'Passion' is a measure of determination in one's SOUL towards something. It is at its highest when, as the name implies, the person experiencing it is suffering for something they believe in. Passion allows the person's SOUL to 'burn brighter', exchanging longevity for raw power. Too much passion can cause a person to burn themselves out, dying cold.",
