    {
      "id": "d8d56ac6-1e1e-4f16-bef3-2790269b5cf9",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**The Primordial**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**The Primordial**\n\nThe Primordial is the fundamental force of the universe, from which all magic is drawn. It is a chaotic and unpredictable force, capable of both creation and destruction. More than mere energy, the Primordial contains the accumulated SOULs of everyone who has ever died — an ocean of consciousness older than thought itself. The beastfolk were the first to harness this energy, using their SOULs as a conduit to access its power. Humans later attempted to replicate this process, though their understanding was incomplete, leading to their diminished capacity for magic.\n\nWhether the Primordial possesses any form of awareness or will remains unknown. Some believe it is sentient, others see it as a natural phenomenon akin to gravity. Regardless, it remains a powerful and mysterious force that continues to shape the world of Terra.",
