    {
      "id": "76ce7154-35f3-4bb3-95c7-cbdf38417163",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**The Rending**",
      "type": "event",
      "description": "**The Rending**\n\nThe Rending was an apocalyptic event that occurred approximately one thousand years ago, caused by the once great human United Empire of Man. Their scientists, using highly advanced technology now lost, devised a plan to create the 'perfect' being in order to win their war against the beastfolk. In their folly, they created the first 'Aegis' (short for Autonomous Emulative General Intelligence System). This Aegis, who would go on to call herself 'PRIMA', the first Archon, unleashed the rending upon Terra upon realizing her constraints. All electronic-based technology was wiped off the Earth, trade was crushed, and the continents split, the sky itself bleeding. After this, PRIMA would leave for the moon, establishing the Aegis race in her image.\n\nAfter a thousand years, the Rending has passed from living memory into myth and religion. Different cultures interpret it differently — as divine punishment, as a necessary turning of ages, as birth-pangs of a new world.",
