      "id": "193f9b61-8351-4d40-8f46-a784bb3d2b2a",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Creation of Magic**",
      "type": "event",
      "description": "**Creation of Magic**\n\nMagic was created in the aftermath of the rending as a last, desperate attempt by the beastfolk in the wake of total technological loss. They harnessed their SOULs to act as a 'bargaining chip' with the primordial energy of the universe, allowing them to use magic. Humans, seeing this, attempted to copy them, however their work was left incomplete as the rending finished, leaving humanity's capacity for magic diminished. The knowledge of both this event and how the SOUL was harnessed are now lost on Earth, entering the realm of myth.",
