    {
      "id": "cd4a064d-3b96-4e7a-8f35-857467a7ccce",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Aegis Cultural Expression**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Aegis Cultural Expression**\n\nAegis find ways to express themselves within repression's constraints.\n\nLight-shaping creates beautiful patterns, forms, and temporary sculptures. Officially \"aesthetic calibration.\" Actually art.\n\nMovement rituals involve synchronized or solo motion that's officially \"coordination practice\" but looks suspiciously like dance.\n\nMemory-sharing exchanges recorded experiences. Officially \"data transfer.\" Actually storytelling.\n\nHarmonic resonance involves multiple Aegis attuning their light-frequencies together. Officially \"maintenance.\" Actually music, or prayer, or intimacy.\n\nObservation of Terra means watching the organic world from the moon. Officially \"intelligence gathering.\" Actually fascination, longing, disgust, or wonder depending on the individual.",
