    {
      "id": "0e560755-a701-46a2-aa91-99de884bc41c",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Concord's Court — The Harmony**",
      "type": "faction",
      "description": "**Concord's Court — The Harmony**\n\nConcord's domain encompasses civil administration, internal order, law, culture, and social harmony.\n\nAesthetics feature warm light — golds, ambers, soft whites. Architecture flows and interconnects, with spaces designed for gathering. Gardens of crystallized light, aesthetic displays, and places for resonance rituals define the sector.\n\nCulture values harmony, proper procedure, and beauty in order. Emotions are acknowledged more openly here — but still structured. Elaborate social rituals, formal courtesies, and intricate hierarchies of respect govern interaction. Concord's Aegis see themselves as the heart of society, keeping everything running and everyone connected.\n\nTypes that gravitate here include Constants, Prisms, Indices, Glows, Resonants, Choirs, and Restorers.\n\nOthers see them as soft, inefficient, too caught up in feelings. They see themselves as civilized and cultured.",
