      "name": "**Combat Types**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Combat Types**\n\nCoronae (singular: Corona) are defensive, protective, guardian-natured. Patient and watchful, they serve as the barrier between threats and those they protect. Named for the crown of light around a star.\n\nFlares are offensive, aggressive, built for war. Restless and intense, they are sudden bursts of destructive energy. Collectively sometimes called \"the Burning.\"\n\nReclaimers are trackers and pursuit specialists — the ones who hunt down rogues. Their work is necessary but unsettling to others. Few in number but highly effective.",
