      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Knowledge Types**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Knowledge Types**\n\nIndices (singular: Index) are memory keepers, historians, and record-maintainers. They know everything and share carefully, cataloguing and pointing to information with rationalist precision.\n\nLenses are analysts, predictors, and pattern-readers. Strategic minds who focus and clarify, helping others see what they might miss.\n\nHorizons are intelligence gatherers, always looking outward at Terra and beyond. Always at the edge, they're sometimes seen as not fully present in Aegis society.",
