      "id": "5b4a0b5c-7bd1-4815-80b5-babb63733acb",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Technical Types**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Technical Types**\n\nForges are builders, engineers, and creators of infrastructure. Practical and proud of their work, they are where light is shaped into purpose.\n\nFilaments are precision specialists, handling delicate work and fine manipulation. Detail-oriented to the point of obsession, they are the delicate threads of light.\n\nRestorers are repair specialists for both structures and other Aegis. The closest thing to doctors, they occupy a strange position — everyone needs them, no one respects the dependency.",
