    {
      "id": "30f91a12-460a-4864-a33b-49a1a3587bc3",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Administrative Types**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Administrative Types**\n\nRays are messengers, communicators, and go-betweens. They carry light and information from source to destination, knowing everyone and trusted by necessity.\n\nConstants are resource managers and logistics specialists, keeping everything running. The unchanging and reliable, they are underappreciated despite being essential.\n\nPrisms are dispute resolvers and rule interpreters. They separate truth from falsehood, breaking things into components. Simultaneously respected and resented.",
