    {
      "id": "74ebe4e5-5013-4f38-93b8-634b295b1733",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Service Types**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Service Types**\n\nGlows are personal attendants to higher-ranked Aegis. Soft, ambient, always present, easy to overlook — they have intimate access but low status, creating a complicated position. They see everything. Sometimes mockingly called \"Dims\" by others.\n\nResonants maintain harmony and keep frequencies aligned. Their work is almost spiritual, ensuring Aegis society stays synchronized.\n\nChoirs are culture-shapers, entertainers, and ritual leaders. Multiple lights in harmony, they shape what Aegis society believes about itself. Rare and influential.",
