    {
      "id": "bb2a7b97-a407-4601-b242-924fe64ce198",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Specialized Types**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Specialized Types**\n\nEmbers are designed for contact with organics on Terra. Rare and viewed as tainted by proximity to lesser beings, their light is diminished to survive among organics. Those who've spent time on Terra are sometimes called \"Dustwalkers.\"\n\nNulls are not designed but emerge — something in their core is wrong. In a society of light-beings, a Null is fundamentally broken in ways that affect others. Officially they don't exist. See separate entry.",
