      "type": "location",
      "description": "**The Zenith — PRIMA's Domain**\n\nThe highest point, literally and symbolically. Few have ever seen it directly. Those summoned there return different — quieter, unwilling to discuss what they experienced. PRIMA's personal attendants, the Zenith Circle, are rarely seen elsewhere. Her domain is not part of the Court system but above it entirely.",
