      "name": "**The Harmony — Concord's Sector**",
      "type": "location",
      "description": "**The Harmony — Concord's Sector**\n\nWarm light suffuses everything — golds, ambers, soft whites. Architecture flows and interconnects, with spaces designed for gathering. Gardens of crystallized light, aesthetic displays, and places for resonance rituals fill the sector. Administrative centers, record halls, and courts of adjudication handle governance. The sector feels alive with social energy, Aegis always moving and interacting. Glows, Constants, Indices, Resonants, and Choirs are seen everywhere.",
