      "name": "**The Bastion — Praxis's Sector**",
      "type": "location",
      "description": "**The Bastion — Praxis's Sector**\n\nCool light dominates — blues, silvers, stark whites. Angular architecture imposes and intimidates, with spaces designed for function. Training grounds, strategic chambers, and observation arrays point toward Terra. Armories hold light-weapons, and barracks station Aegis even though they don't truly sleep. The sector feels purposeful, everyone moving with direction. Coronae, Flares, Lenses, and Horizons are seen everywhere.",
