      "description": "**August's Sector — Unnamed**\n\nStill being established, with construction ongoing. Currently a strange mix of inherited spaces being reshaped. Some areas feel like Concord, some like Praxis, some like neither. August herself keeps rearranging things, experimenting. Her Aegis are making it up as they go. Visitors from established Courts find it unsettling — where are the rules?",
