      "type": "location",
      "description": "**Shared Spaces**\n\nThe Convergence is neutral ground where Courts meet, disputes are formally mediated, and joint operations are planned.\n\nThe Forges are where new Aegis are created. Technically neutral but politically charged during allocation of new creations.\n\nThe Arrays are observation and communication systems staffed by both Courts.\n\nThe Memorial is a place where lights that have gone out are remembered. Officially Aegis don't mourn. No one calls it a memorial. But it exists.",
