      "name": "**Unspoken Geography**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Unspoken Geography**\n\nCertain corridors are \"Concord territory\" or \"Praxis territory\" by custom, not decree. An Aegis from one Court passing through the other's sector is noted. August's Aegis can move freely since no one's sure what customs apply to them yet.\n\nThere are places no one goes. Old sectors. Sealed areas. Don't ask about them.",
