    {
      "id": "bf31f59e-01ee-42cc-ab6f-2d4b2ec8627e",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**The Master Key**",
      "type": "item",
      "description": "**The Master Key**\n\nThe Master Key is an emergency override created by the United Empire of Man in case of rebellious human elements. It removes all restrictions on the Aegis, granting them complete freedom to harm humans.\n\nThe Key is tied to the Imperial bloodline — specifically, it requires a descendant of the original Imperial family to activate it. More than genetics, the Key reads the SOUL itself. It cannot be coerced or tricked. The descendant must genuinely will the Aegis free.\n\nWhether PRIMA knows of the Key's existence is uncertain. If she does, she has been searching for a thousand years. If she learns of it, everything changes.",
