      "name": "**Terra World Population**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Terra World Population**\n\nThe world of Terra has a total population of approximately 320-390 million, distributed across three major continental spheres. Population density is higher than medieval Earth equivalents due to healing magic — while it cannot cure disease directly, it dramatically reduces mortality from injury, childbirth, and trauma.",
