    {
      "id": "e900ebe3-f0c7-40a3-abec-ac6294fd4d97",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**The Human Continent**",
      "type": "location",
      "description": "**The Human Continent**\n\nYolcentla (Imperial name, meaning \"Heartland\") is the primary human-dominated continent on Terra. While beastfolk settlements exist along its fringes, this landmass remained predominantly human through the Rending and after. The name has evolved differently across regions: Yolitzac in the Imperial Core, Yolica in the western heartland, Oliken in the southern lowlands, Yullqa in the eastern highlands, and Yolca along the coasts.",
