      "name": "**Other Human Kingdoms**",
      "type": "faction",
      "description": "**Other Human Kingdoms**\n\nSeveral human kingdoms exist outside Yolcentla, though they never reach the glory that the United Empire of Man once had. Relevant kingdoms include:\n\n**The Kingdom of Lucia:** A naval kingdom located near the port of a large beastfolk city-state. They are known for their skilled sailors and traders, often acting as intermediaries between beastfolk and human settlements.\n\n**The Kingdom of Skaros:** A militaristic kingdom located in a harsh desert region on Tieravel. They are known for their fierce warriors and strict discipline, often hiring out their soldiers as mercenaries.",
