    {
      "id": "cf898ffd-3413-4a1c-94eb-3cdc04392af5",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Technology on Terra**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Technology on Terra**\n\nTechnology on Terra is a mix of salvaged pre-Rending technology and newly developed tech by the beastfolk and humans. The Rending wiped out all electronic-based technology, leaving only mechanical and steam-powered devices. However, some remnants of pre-Rending technology still exist, often highly prized and sought after. The Aegis possess highly advanced technology, far beyond that of the beastfolk and humans, though they do not operate magic-based technology like Terrans do. The beastfolk and humans have developed their own technology, often using magic to augment their devices. This has led to a unique blend of magic and technology, with devices such as enchanted weapons, magical communication devices, and steam-powered vehicles being common. However, the overall level of technology on Terra is still relatively low compared to pre-Rending levels, with many areas still relying on basic tools and manual labor.",
