    {
      "id": "3ffeb27c-aa28-488f-997e-73b11fb916a5",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**The Umbral Order**",
      "type": "faction",
      "description": "**The Umbral Order**\n\nThe Umbral Order is a secret society of magic users, both beastfolk and humans, who seek to uncover the true nature of magic and the SOUL. They believe that magic is not simply a tool to be used, but a fundamental force of the universe that can be harnessed and understood. The Umbral Order is highly secretive, with members often operating in the shadows and using code names to protect their identities.\n\nTheir secret, ultimate goal is to find a way to merge the SOULs of all beings, creating a single, unified consciousness that can transcend the limitations of individual existence. They believe that this will lead to 'enlightenment'.\n\nThis goal makes them uniquely dangerous. If they ever published their findings about SOUL mechanics, or if PRIMA placed a spy within their ranks, the knowledge could provide the breakthrough the Aegis need to circumvent their constraints.",
