      "id": "6885aacb-dc9a-4588-91dd-861247feebdf",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**The Zhiran Continent**",
      "type": "location",
      "description": "**The Zhiran Continent**\n\nThe second major continent of Terra, dominated by the river civilization of Zhiran and its cultural sphere. Unlike Yolcentla, where humans dominate, this continent features significant integration between humans and beastfolk — though the nature of that integration varies dramatically by region. The continent also borders the steppe territories of Göran and the mountainous homeland of Drakhar, whose peoples are considered \"barbarian\" by the river civilization.",
