    {
      "id": "27535321-3b6f-44a4-bae8-3f88a8a8dfbe",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Zhongliu**",
      "type": "location",
      "description": "**Zhongliu**\n\nZhongliu (Central Flow) is the heartland of Zhiran, the river valley itself. Dense population, intensive agriculture, and the great cities define this region. This is where the Five Natures ideology actually works — species mixing in markets, intermarriage not uncommon, examination culture dominant.\n\nMajor cities include Heyang (the capital), Hekou (River Mouth, a major trading city at a tributary confluence), and Changdi (Long Embankment, famous for flood control engineering).\n\nThe region's issues are complacency, corruption masked by proper forms, and growing disconnect between court and reality.",
