      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Xishan**",
      "type": "location",
      "description": "**Xishan**\n\nXishan (Western Mountains) faces Drakhar. Rugged terrain, traditional culture, and quiet heterodoxy define the region. Old ways persist beneath official culture.\n\nMajor cities include Yanmen (Smoke Gate, controlling the main pass into the mountains) and Qinglin (Green Forest, a lumber and mining town).\n\nThe autonomous zone of Yunjian (Cloud Valley) is a remote highland valley technically part of Xishan but practically self-governing, with mixed human and beastfolk population following their own syncretic traditions.\n\nFewer Elaphines live here as they dislike the terrain. More humans and Felines — some \"civilized\" Felines have dwelt here for generations, serving as intermediaries during peace and intelligence sources during conflict. Lungta raids are a fact of life. If Zhiran invades Drakhar, these people will suffer Feline retaliation first.",
