    {
      "id": "aae1e1de-ee4f-4483-b835-140709ea9615",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Mohe Reaches**",
      "type": "location",
      "description": "**Mohe Reaches**\n\nThe Mohe Reaches form the far northern frontier, barely administered. Scattered settlements, trading posts, and seasonal camps define the region rather than major cities.\n\nHumans, Lupines who have left Göran, and mixed-ancestry people who do not fit anywhere else live here. Everyone has a past they are not discussing. Zhiran authority extends as far as the last tax collector was willing to travel.",
