      "name": "**Goryun Population**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Goryun Population**\n\nHumans form the majority at roughly 75-80%, serving as the political ruling class and filling most roles. Elaphines comprise roughly 15%, living in valley communities and serving in bureaucracy, trade, and logistics. Some noble Elaphine families have long histories. Felines comprise roughly 5%, living in eastern mountain communities, more isolated and autonomous, serving as scouts, border guards, and mountain rangers.",
