    {
      "id": "627eb565-85ea-4478-ba97-33141cc38e9b",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Goryun Military**",
      "type": "faction",
      "description": "**Goryun Military**\n\nThe nation takes defense seriously, maintaining a standing professional army unlike Zhiran's neglected conscripts. Military service is honorable even for nobles. The Hwarang are elite warrior-scholars who embody Jeongyeol, trained in both philosophy and combat.\n\nHumans serve as infantry, cavalry, navy, and most officers. Elaphines handle logistics and siege engineering. Felines serve as scouts and mountain warfare specialists. The nation can defend but cannot project power far due to limited population and resources.",
