    {
      "id": "2f5d21ed-0ef3-4299-9ab8-b5160a329f9f",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Aohane**",
      "type": "faction",
      "description": "**Aohane**\n\nAohane (Blue Feather Isles) is an archipelago nation inhabited by the Pavonines, the only avian beastfolk on Terra. They are a civilization apart — sharing some cultural elements with Zhiran through selective adoption, but fundamentally different in nature and philosophy.\n\nThe islands are mountainous and volcanic, mist-shrouded and dramatic. The sea around them is treacherous, with strong currents and hidden rocks protecting them from invasion. They have never been conquered.",
