    {
      "id": "af501239-9579-4e80-a76c-d4c007ece1f9",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**The Thalassic Sphere**",
      "type": "location",
      "description": "**The Thalassic Sphere**\n\nThe southern and eastern coasts wrap around the warm, calm inner sea. This region is human-majority, trade-focused, and organized into city-states and merchant republics. The humans here developed around the polis — the idea that civilization itself is humanity's great work. The city is sacred. Law is sacred. The SOUL finds its highest expression not in solitary cultivation but in civic participation.",
