      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Yolica (The Heartland Kingdoms)**\n\nYolica shares the Solar Faith but interprets it differently: less anxious dualism, more cyclical acceptance. Magic is understood as \"feeding the age\"—each SOUL-bargain sustains the current world-cycle. The focus is on participation in cosmic maintenance rather than fearful vigilance against darkness.",
