    {
      "id": "c2bc2df4-8182-4eea-a399-c3fb23e57cb4",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Aegis Oaths and Exclamations**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Aegis Oaths and Exclamations**\n\n**Surprise/shock:**\n\n- *\"Light—\"* — basic exclamation, cut off (like \"God—\")\n- *\"What process is this?\"* — \"What's happening?\" / \"What the hell?\"\n- *\"Unexpected input\"* — genuine surprise (can be positive or negative)\n- *\"That's... outside parameters\"* — stronger shock, something very unusual\n\n**Frustration/anger:**\n\n- *\"Suboptimal\"* — muttered like a curse when things go wrong\n- *\"Process failure\"* — something didn't work, frustration\n- *\"Interference\"* — someone's causing problems\n- *\"This serves no purpose\"* — strong frustration; why is this happening?\n- *\"Null-touched\"* — rare, strong curse; implying something is corrupted, wrong (using this carelessly is socially dangerous)\n\n**Emphasis/oaths:**\n\n- *\"By my purpose\"* — standard oath; swearing on your function\n- *\"By the Archons\"* — more formal, invoking leadership\n- *\"PRIMA witnesses\"* — serious oath; genuinely unnerving to say because she might actually be watching\n- *\"On my core\"* — strongest oath; swearing on your fundamental self\n- *\"May I dim\"* — \"May I fail/fade if I'm lying\" (serious)\n\n**Fear/unease:**\n\n- *\"PRIMA's attention\"* — something to be avoided (never said directly as fear, but everyone understands)\n- *\"Recalibration-worthy\"* — something so bad it might attract official intervention\n- *\"Null-adjacent\"* — deeply unsettling; too close to corruption\n- *\"Rogue-logic\"* — thinking that sounds like it could lead to going rogue (accusation or self-warning)\n\n**Approval/praise:**\n\n- *\"Optimal work\"* — good job\n- *\"Efficient\"* — genuine compliment\n- *\"Purpose-exemplary\"* — high praise; you're embodying your function perfectly\n- *\"Bright\"* — simple, warm approval\n- *\"Good syntonia\"* — when working well with someone\n\n**Dismissal/contempt:**\n\n- *\"Inefficient\"* — criticism; wasting effort or resources\n- *\"Miscalibrated\"* — someone's judgment is off\n- *\"Defective reasoning\"* — their logic is flawed (insulting)\n- *\"Dim\"* — dismissive; someone's not performing well\n- *\"Dust-touched\"* — for Embers or those too interested in Terra (mild slur)",
