      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**What Oliken City-States Get Wrong**\n\n**\"Our Hero Twins prophecy is unique.\"** Every Oliken city believes their version is the true one. None of them acknowledge that the prophecy has been reinterpreted dozens of times, or that the original meaning (if there was one) is lost.\n\n**\"Lakamtun are mercenary traitors.\"** Other Oliken cities despise Lakamtun for hiring out soldiers to beastfolk. They conveniently ignore that Lakamtun's mountain position makes them the only thing preventing certain trade routes from collapse.",
