    {
      "id": "2308e2eb-7431-4be9-af54-cbd161977fbd",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**What Others Believe About Aohane**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**What Others Believe About Aohane**\n\n**\"They are hiding something.\"** Everyone is right about this—Aohane guards many secrets. But the specific theories are usually wrong. They are not secretly planning invasion. They are not stockpiling weapons. The secrets are more likely spiritual and historical than military.\n\n**\"Their magic is illusion and trickery.\"** Zhiran scholars tend to dismiss Aohane's wind and light magic as impressive but insubstantial. This underestimates both its combat applications and its spiritual depth.\n\n**\"The Pavonines were created by the Empire.\"** A persistent theory that the Pavonines find deeply offensive. No evidence supports it, but the mystery of their origin invites speculation.",
