      "name": "**Yolcentla About Tieravel**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Yolcentla About Tieravel**\n\n**\"The beastfolk there are the same as everywhere.\"** Yolcentla has almost no contact with Tieravel, but assumes beastfolk are beastfolk. The idea that Tieravel beastfolk have radically different cultures, religions, and politics from anything in the Zhiran sphere does not occur to them.\n\n**\"Humans there are lost cousins.\"** There is vague awareness that humans live across the sea, but no understanding that Thalassic culture has developed entirely independently, with different gods, different magic, different everything.",
