    {
      "id": "9d5785f1-b800-494d-877d-5a057ec85475",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Tieravel About Yolcentla**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Tieravel About Yolcentla**\n\n**\"The human continent is unified.\"** Rumors reach Tieravel of a great human landmass. The internal divisions—Yolitzac versus Yolica, Oliken city-state rivalries, Yullqa's independence—are unknown. The continent is imagined as one Empire.\n\n**\"Their magic is sacrificial blood-cult.\"** The stories that reach Tieravel emphasize the most dramatic elements of Solar Faith practice. The subtle theology, the regional variations, the sophisticated philosophy—none of this penetrates. Yolcentla is imagined as priests cutting out hearts over pyramids.",
