    {
      "id": "6888f97f-64bd-40dd-b939-cf44e1f20869",
      "storyId": "55fed642-2517-4046-865d-17e3ade46d48",
      "name": "**Everyone About Everyone**",
      "type": "concept",
      "description": "**Everyone About Everyone**\n\n**\"We understand the Rending.\"** No one does. Every culture has myths about what happened a thousand years ago. The truth—that humans created the Aegis, that PRIMA shattered the world, that magic was invented in desperation—is lost. What remains are stories shaped by each culture's needs.\n\n**\"Our way is the natural way.\"** Every civilization believes its values are universal, its customs are correct, its understanding of the SOUL is accurate. None of them consider that they might all be grasping different parts of the same incomprehensible truth.",
